{"tid":1674047,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"11月港殤紀念，全民戴花 – 以黃花紀念義士","createTime":"2019-10-25T03:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T07:13:11.000Z","uid":116278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e3f73ebde68b7cff179570a1a57f4984afa7ba1d","tid":1674047,"uid":116278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:41:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">11月港殤紀念，全民戴花 &ndash; 以黃花紀念義士</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國殤紀念日</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">(Remembrance Day)</span></span></strong> 訂立於每年的 11 月 11 日，為一個由英聯邦國家紀念在一戰、二戰和其他戰爭中犧牲的軍人與平民的紀念節日，又稱「和平紀念日」、「陣亡將士紀念日」。<br />\n<br />\n國殤紀念日一般會佩戴一種紅色的虞美人花（和罌粟花同屬不同種），佩戴的原因來自加拿大軍醫John McCrae的一首詩《在法蘭德斯戰場 (In Flanders Fields) 》，虞美人花被選擇是因為一戰最慘烈的戰場法蘭德斯盛開着虞美人花，而虞美人花的紅色代表壕溝中的鮮血。後來亦有人佩戴白色的罌粟花，他們認為這代表和平。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">虞美人花</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/fDmTOM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2FfDmTOM.jpg&h=20fb428f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">In Flanders fields the poppies blow<br />\nBetween the crosses, row on row,<br />\n  That mark our place; and in the sky<br />\n  The larks, still bravely singing, fly<br />\nScarce heard amid the guns below.<br />\n<br />\nWe are the Dead. Short days ago<br />\nWe lived, felt dawn, saw sunset glow,<br />\n  Loved and were loved, and now we lie<br />\n      In Flanders fields.<br />\n<br />\nTake up our quarrel with the foe:<br />\nTo you from failing hands we throw<br />\n  The torch; be yours to hold it high.<br />\n  If ye break faith with us who die<br />\nWe shall not sleep, though poppies grow<br />\n      In Flanders fields.</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K6BlOkpdkg8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK6BlOkpdkg8&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTUzY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=b1290911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K6BlOkpdkg8</a><br />\n<br />\n我們團隊製作了一個黃色虞美人花襟針的設計圖，大家除了紀念當年英勇保衛香港的軍人，亦希望同時可以紀念近五個月以來，因反送中運動受傷、折騰，甚至結束自己生命的朋友。<br />\n<br />\n簡單版<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/3N9nue.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2F3N9nue.jpg&h=f853a174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n進階版<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/jFv3WU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2FjFv3WU.jpg&h=50d0f39a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十一月香港人要繼續遍地開花，讓極權政府知道我們並不會因惡法、施政報告無用的小恩小惠而退縮！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mgELDYH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmgELDYH.jpg&h=da5355cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c09Pmb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc09Pmb3.jpg&h=0e8b50c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十一月,齊上齊落齊FORWARD!<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/A9QSLf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2FA9QSLf.jpg&h=092e0f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n初階版LINK:<br />\n<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/3N9nue.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2F3N9nue.jpg&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTUzY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=9a85a28f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/3N9nue.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n進階版LINK:<br />\n]<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/jFv3WU.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2FjFv3WU.jpg&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTUzY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=46466edf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/25/jFv3WU.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"689402b0137f64f9da2c4608d0be67d8e3f35141","tid":1674047,"uid":116278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:48:48.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"81f27172d10e5803e83c2f340afcb1c71e2b7dba","tid":1674047,"uid":116278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"11月港殤紀念，全民戴花 &ndash; 以黃花紀念義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1674052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1674052</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b733d6f30a1d85cb3a01f1865ab982ac45df5135","tid":1674047,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T07:13:11.000Z","msg":"推"}]}